===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|archaic}} make a memorial speech; to [[eulogize]]
#* {{zh-x|夏 四月 己丑，^孔-丘 卒，公 '''誄''' 之 曰，旻天 不 弔，不 憖 遺 一 老，俾 屏 余一人 以 在 位，煢煢 余 在 疚，嗚呼 哀哉，^尼-父 無 自 律！|On the eleventh day in the fourth month during summer, {{w|Kong Qiu}} died. Duke Ai of Lu '''gave his memorial speech''' as follows: "Heaven is not willing to let this veteran minister protect me and remains me, the only one, alone. Father Zhongni [Kong Qiu] is gone and Father Zhongni has gone! I have lost the laws to administer my government!"|ref=Zuozhuan-D}}
# {{lb|zh|archaic}} a [[eulogy]] of the dead
#* {{zh-x|（^宝-玉）所以 大肆 妄誕，竟 杜撰 成 一 篇 長文，用 ^晴-雯 素日 所 喜 之 冰 鮫 縠 一 幅 楷 字 寫 成，名 曰《芙蓉 女兒 誄》，前 序 後 歌。|So giving free rein to his absurd imagination, he made up a long lament, and he copied this out neatly on a white translucent silk kerchief which Ching-wen had fancied, entitling it '''''Elegy''' for the Hibiscus Maid'' and giving it preface and a concluding song.|ref=Hongloumeng}}

